<h2>About the EP</h2>
<div class="content-box">
    <p><a href="http://thisislsr.com">Leeds Student Radio</a> is excited to announce that we will be producing a live-album in association with <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ComePlayWith/">Come Play With Me</a> called 'Picture House Sessions'!</p>
    <p>This ambitious project will feature five incredible bands: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/kumikoknew/">Kumiko</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/talkboyyy/">Talkboy, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Jabbawoki.Leeds/">Jabbawoki</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/laminatepetanimalmusic/">Laminate Pet Animal</a> and <a href="https://www.facebook.com/theseagulls/">The Seagulls</a>.</p>
    <p>We are delighted to announce that <a href="https://www.facebook.com/TheHydeParkPictureHouse/">The Hyde Park Picture House</a> are letting us record the album at their prestigious location on the 15th of February which you can watch!</p>
    <p>The audience are invited to join us from 11am till 4pm with (Â£2) tickets being sold on the door and pre-order of the album available.</p>
    <p>Alternatively, you can pick-up a ticket in advance at LSR's event - The Transmission 2018! You can find the event <a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/113836279425319/">here</a>.</p>
    <p>The album will be released on the 27th of April, with a launch event to be announced soon!</p>
</div>